"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1928185-Elena-Rybakina-Olympics-statement\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Elena Rybakinahas revealed that she was banned from travelling to theOlympicsby her doctors after contracting 'acute bronchitis'.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_of_The_Wire\", \"score\": 0.9999999984793249, \"rank\": 1.517478840215937e-09, \"text\": \"Elena\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_of_The_Wire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_of_The_Wire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old was due to represent Kazakhstan in the women's singles and mixed doublesbut withdrew just hours after the draw was made on Thursday.Rybakina has struggled with illness over the course of this year, having withdrawn from a number of high-profile events over the last few months.\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 169, \"end\": 179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\", \"score\": 0.9998953148526047, \"rank\": 0.00010412253275572952, \"text\": \"Kazakhstan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She pulled out of the Dubai Open, Indian Wells and the Italian Open as well as the Eastbourne International in the run-up toWimbledon.Explaining her decision to skip the Olympics on medical grounds, she revealed that her doctors 'forbade' her from travelling to Paris or playing tennis in spite of her efforts to recover in time.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Wells_Masters\", \"score\": 0.9975966749022993, \"rank\": 0.002409112104420182, \"text\": \"Indian Wells\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Wells_Masters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Wells_Masters\"}, {\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastbourne_International\", \"score\": 0.9997585125405098, \"rank\": 0.00024154255507313776, \"text\": \"Eastbourne International\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastbourne_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eastbourne_International\"}, {\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999773212951, \"rank\": 2.267867829717817e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  In a statement posted onInstagram, Rybakina said: \\\"It is hard for me to tell you this, but unfortunately, I will not be able to take part in the Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1207, \"end\": 1212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999773212951, \"rank\": 2.267867829717817e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the Wimbledon tournament, I fell ill with acute bronchitis, and despite attempts to return to training, my body has not yet recovered.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Doctors forbade me to go out on the court.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very sorry that I will not be able to justify your hopes and compete for our team at the Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999773212951, \"rank\": 2.267867829717817e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was so close to a medal in Tokyo and carefully prepared for the Paris Games to win gold for Kazakhstan.Unfortunately, illness prevented these plans from coming true.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9075133915590375, \"rank\": 0.10190904300867988, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wish all Kazakhstani athletes good luck and success in Paris.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1736, \"end\": 1741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999773212951, \"rank\": 2.267867829717817e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will root for all our athletes and believe that they will be able to worthily represent our country at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alga, Kazakhstan!\\\"\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1880, \"entit